### Account entity HTTP tests
### Account 전용 컨트롤러는 없어서 Subscription 흐름을 통해 간접 검증합니다.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userEmail = user1@test.com
@userPassword = 12345678
@firstProductAccountNumber = 30100010002
@secondProductAccountNumber = 30100010003

### User 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("user_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### Account 간접 생성: 상품 가입 시 상품 계좌 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "accountNumber": "{{firstProductAccountNumber}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("account_subscription_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### Account 간접 조회: 내 가입 내역에서 계좌번호 포맷 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Account 간접 잔액 증가: 자유입출금 계좌에서 상품 계좌로 이체
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriptionId": {{account_subscription_id}},
  "amount": 10000,
  "fromAccountNumber": "12345678901"
}

### Account 비정상 테스트: 중복 계좌번호로 상품 가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 2,
  "accountNumber": "{{firstProductAccountNumber}}"
}

### Account 비정상 테스트: 존재하지 않는 출금 계좌로 이체
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriptionId": {{account_subscription_id}},
  "amount": 10000,
  "fromAccountNumber": "99999999999"
}

### Account 추가 생성 예시: 다른 상품 계좌 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 7,
  "accountNumber": "{{secondProductAccountNumber}}"
}

